{"type":"message","id":"fe8b8a97","parentId":"dba5216e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:45:27.986Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-04-03 09:45 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务相关行业的最新动态（2026年），整理3-5条关键信息，保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}],"timestamp":1775180727983}}
{"type":"message","id":"102f42fe","parentId":"fe8b8a97","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:45:34.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for the latest industry news about enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services in 2026.","thinkingSignature":"bcc4c0e4ddf154e11fec9cb70ff55d832753ed4c1fb6c66dcf592fd0ce1c294d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s2u91jtn1q2j_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":69,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42011,"totalTokens":42197,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0000828,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.005041319999999999,"total":0.005159219999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775180727984}}
{"type":"message","id":"06478983","parentId":"102f42fe","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:45:34.759Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s2u91jtn1q2j_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775180734756}}
{"type":"message","id":"af85e4b2","parentId":"06478983","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:45:40.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for the latest industry news about enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services in 2026.","thinkingSignature":"ea7b94da37c1cfc00a23b4be6b77758f6eed21b33bc9b1542555616cd0d21212"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_urpku86ow4ov_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新动态 趋势\" 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_urpku86ow4ov_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2026 行业发展趋势 最新政策\" 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_urpku86ow4ov_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026 行业动态\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":811,"output":170,"cacheRead":41901,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42882,"cost":{"input":0.00024329999999999998,"output":0.000204,"cacheRead":0.00125703,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00170433}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775180734759}}
